#compdef distcc
# Documentation: https://www.distcc.org/man/distcc_1.html
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# distcc client flags from the distcc(1) man page. Note: most positional args
# are forwarded to the wrapped compiler, so we dispatch to cc completion.

_arguments \
  '--help[show help message]' \
  '--version[show version]' \
  '--show-hosts[show host list distcc would use]' \
  '--scan-includes[show files distcc would send (pump mode)]' \
  '--show-principal[show distccd security principal from environment]' \
  '-j[show concurrency level from host list]' \
  '*::compiler arguments:_dispatch cc cc'
